Priority: optional
Maintainer: Torsten Werner <twerner@debian.org>
Standards-Version: 3.9.0
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), indent, libattr1-dev, libpam0g-dev
Homepage: http://sites.google.com/site/fullycapable/
